cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with computer vision and human-computer interaction, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques and models, which fall under the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves eye tracking and visual attention, which are relevant to the sub-categories cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
